Now, what happens if we include a spline term on age?

`vfit2 <- coxph(Surv(time, status) ~ trt + splines::ns(age,3), vdata1)`


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
# Refit model with spline on age
vfit2 <- coxph(Surv(time, status) ~ trt + splines::ns(age,3), vdata1)
tbl_regression(vfit2, exp = T)
```

